'''Maizie's''' was a [[Tapcafe/Legends|tapcafe]] that was located on the [[Planet/Legends|world]] of [[Mandrine/Legends|Mandrine]]. It was in this bar that [[Captain/Legends|Captain]] [[Scarlet Bloodhawk]] met many beings, including [[Kelly Vermillion]], [[Tyric (Shaliz'Na)|Tyric]], [[Nana]], [[Spy 189|Red]], [[Justice (bounty hunter)|Justice]] and [[Truth]]. While he was talking to Kelly and his gang, a thug known as [[Kronus]] entered the bar with his goons and proceeded to cause a brawl. During the fight he was killed in the explosion from a [[Thermal detonator/Legends|thermal detonator]], dropped by one of his dead dupes, of whom all were killed. Maizie's wasn't clean for weeks afterwards.

